   "source": [
    "Ques 13: What can you do to save a programme from crashing if it encounters an error?\n",
    "\n",
    "Answer:\n",
    "# Place the line of code in the try clause, when it causes an error."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "cc6f7811-71cb-407a-a441-1ac0e189c8b1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Ques 14: What is the purpose of the try clause? What is the purpose of the except clause?\n",
    "\n",
    "Answer:\n",
    "# The purpose of try clause is testing the block of code for errors.\n",
    "\n",
    "# The purpose of except clause is to handle the error."
   ]
  }
